snippet.title: A Corgi's Cozy Hike - Official Trailer | The MIX | Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2025
snippet.description: Dive into the colorful world of A Corgi's Cozy Hike in this trailer for the upcoming cozy, open-world 3D platformer game. A Corgi's Cozy Hike will be available on PC, and a demo is out now. EmBARK on a therapeutic vacation! Collect Corgi Butt Power to prove stubby legs can't stop you from climbing and soaring your way to Serenity Summit - stopping for tasty treats and cozy nap spots along the way.
